                                        "},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"There 6 ways to form the numbers 1, 2 and 3 into a three-digit number: 123, 132, 213, 231, 312, and 321. Of these numbers, there are only two even numbers, 132 and 312. Therefore the answer is 2."}]},{"type":"text","text":"



