{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"




                                        "},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Since we want to get even numbers, 2 should be the unit digit. Thus, we are left with 1 and 3, which yields 2 permutations, i.e. (1,3) and (3,1). In conclusion, there are only 2 numbers, 132 and 312."}]},{"type":"text","text":"



                            "}]}

